            <title><![CDATA[关于征集【Hi-Tier】“留学微榜样”系列风采展示作品的通知]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[关于征集【Hi-Tier】“留学微榜样”系列风采展示作品的通知]]></description>
            <link>https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/24/121144</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/24/121144</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 24 Apr 2025 05:11:59 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded>&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;亲爱的2025届毕业生同学们：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Dear Class of 2025 Graduates,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;为营造积极向上的校园氛围，搭建留学经验交流平台，学院特别开展【Hi-Tier】“留学微榜样”风采展示活动，面向全体2025届毕业生征集成长故事。无论你是选择扎根中国继续深造的跨国学子，还是即将满载而归的归国英才，请用文字镌刻奋斗足迹，以光影定格青春记忆，用你的故事传递力量，以榜样之光点亮前行之路！&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;To foster a positive campus atmosphere and create a platform for sharing study abroad experiences, the College is launching the【Hi-Tier】&quot;Study Abroad Role Models&quot; feature showcase. We invite all 2025 graduates to share your growth stories. Whether you are an international student continuing your journey in China or returning home with achievements, let your words immortalize your struggles and your photos capture youthful memories. Share your story to inspire others and light the way forward with your example!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.15pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;一、展示内容&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Submission Content&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;1. 【自我介绍】Self-Introduction&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:48px&quot;&gt;基本信息：姓名/学院（部）/专业/年级&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:48px&quot;&gt;成长勋章：GPA亮点、奖学金、竞赛荣誉等&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:48px&quot;&gt;世界足迹：国际志愿服务、跨文化实践经历&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:48px&quot;&gt;未来坐标：深造院校/回国发展规划（已获录取请注明院校及专业；已就业请注明就业国家及公司全称）&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:48px&quot;&gt;Basic Info: Name/School/Department/Major/Graduation Year&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:48px&quot;&gt;Achievements: GPA highlights, scholarships, competition honors, etc.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:48px&quot;&gt;Global Footprint: International volunteer work, cross-cultural experiences&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-left:48px&quot;&gt;Future Plans: Further education (list admitted institutions and majors) or career plans (specify country and company name if employed)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;2. 【经验分享】Experience Sharing&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;学习规划、语言备考、科研竞赛等实用干货&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;时间管理、跨文化适应、心理调适等成长感悟&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Practical tips on study planning, language test preparation, and research competitions&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Reflections on time management, cross-cultural adaptation, and mental resilience&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;3. 【毕业寄语】Graduation Message&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;对学弟学妹的暖心鼓励或对母校的深情告白&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Heartfelt encouragement for juniors or a tribute to your alma mater&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.15pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;二、内容规格&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Submission Guidelines&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;1. 文字稿件：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;800-1200字（中英文皆可，中英文双语更佳）&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Written Content:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;800-1200 words (Chinese or English; bilingual submissions preferred)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;2. 影像资料：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;个人风采照2张（自然大方，体现个人风格）；&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;校园记忆照2张（图书馆、实验室、操场、校门等地标性背景）。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Visual Materials:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;2 personal portraits (natural and expressive)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;2 campus memory photos (landmark backgrounds like the library, lab, sports field, or school gate)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;3. 提交方式：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;邮箱：&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:20230264l@hit.edu.cn&quot;&gt;20230264l@hit.edu.cn&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;邮件标题：【Hi-Tier】留学微榜样+学号+姓名&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Submission Method:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Email: 20230264l@hit.edu.cn&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Subject:【Hi-Tier】Study Abroad Role Model + Student ID + Name&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;4. 截止时间：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;2025年4月30日24:00&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Deadline:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;April 30, 2025, 24:00&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.15pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;三、你将获得&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;What You’ll Gain&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;1. 个人风采将通过学院官方平台展示；&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Feature on the College’s official platforms&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;2. 有机会参与【Hi-Topic】校友面对面活动，与学弟学妹深度互动；&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Opportunity to participate in [Hi-Topic] Alumni Face-to-Face events for deep interaction with juniors&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;text-align:left; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;3. 投稿作品被录用者可获学院定制版冰箱贴，录用结果与纪念品领取时间地点将于5月10日24:00前通过邮箱发送。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;text-align:left; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;Selected submissions will receive a customized college fridge magnet. Results and pickup details will be emailed by May 10, 2025, 24:00.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;text-align:left; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;四、注意事项&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;Notes&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;投稿即视为同意学校用于非商业宣传。请确保内容真实、原创，投稿内容学院将会进行细微修改。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Submissions imply consent for non-commercial use by the school. Ensure content is authentic and original, minor edits may be made by the College.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;快来投稿，让你的故事成为照亮他人的星光！&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:32.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Submit now and let your story shine as a guiding light for others!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; style=&quot;text-align:right; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;国际教育学院&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; style=&quot;text-align:right; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;学生工作办公室&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; style=&quot;text-align:right; text-indent:32.0pt&quot;&gt;2025年4月24日&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;College of International Education&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;Student Affairs Office&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p align=&quot;right&quot; style=&quot;text-align:right&quot;&gt;April 24, 2025&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded>
        </item>
